{
  "stem": "23428.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I'm pretty sure that was the only-- if-- if at all, that was the only group that showed any solidarity whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The atmosphere in the camp was such that everybody was out for their own survival.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if it was a question of-- of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] listening in to what your neighbors in the bed said, it would immediately be handed on so that-- for personal profit.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You couldn't trust anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And nobody trusted anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, the first-- the first brutality, I think, I saw was, in fact, by the-- in a-- in a-- in a work group that had to do with street construction.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's actually interesting, because it was actually led-- led by the social democrat from Frankfurt I told you about.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was a guy was actually crippled and walked with a-- with a-- with a cane and used this cane extensively on the backs of the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The reason was that he was given a quota for street construction every day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "His superiors, the SS whom we never saw, obviously told him he had to finish in a day two kilometers of street.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And since it was impossible to do by normal means, he simply beat his workers until he had his two kilometers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That means, for another day, he saved his own neck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Hadn't he fulfilled his quota, that would have been the last day he would've been a kapo.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were a lot of advantages, of course, of being a kapo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So-- so that was the general-- that-- that was one of 'em.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And of course, then another thing I remember were, you know, you-- you kept your shoes and your clothes under the hay where you slept, because otherwise everybody would steal it.",
      "word_count": 31
    }
  ],
